Definition: a redeeming quality or characteristic
Example: her love of music remains her one saving grace; her sense of humor has to be a saving grace; the saving grace for both developments is that they are creating jobs
Synonyms: characteristic, a, redeeming, quality, or, her, love, of, music, remains, one, saving, grace, sense, humor, has, to, be, the, for, both, developments, is, that, they, are, creating, jobs
Category: noun.attribute
